# Abenteuer-Spaziergänger - Version 1.0

**Release Date:** 2026-01-06  
**Status:** Stable, Production-Ready

---

## What's Included

This is the first stable release of the **ES Modules refactored** version of Abenteuer-Spaziergänger.

### Architecture
- ✅ Modular ES6 architecture (9 files, ~539 LOC)
- ✅ Clear separation of concerns (State, Router, UI, Logic, Data)
- ✅ Hash-based navigation
- ✅ Modal-based UI (no blocking `window.prompt()`)
- ✅ LocalStorage persistence

### Features
- ✅ Multi-group management (create, rename, delete, switch)
- ✅ Character creation (manual + random generator)
- ✅ Character stat tracking (HP, Wille)
- ✅ Character equipment (3 slots per character)
- ✅ Shared group inventory (12 slots)
- ✅ Quest generator (4 environments)
- ✅ Inspiration generator (dynamic item suggestions)
- ✅ Dark/Light theme toggle
- ✅ PWA support (offline-capable)

### Files
```
version-1.0/
├── index.html              # Main HTML (323 lines)
├── manifest.json           # PWA manifest
├── service-worker.js       # PWA offline support
└── js/
    ├── main.js             # Entry point (55 lines)
    ├── state.js            # State management (41 lines)
    ├── router.js           # Navigation (45 lines)
    ├── data/
    │   └── inspiration.js  # Static data (34 lines)
    └── modules/
        ├── modal.js        # Modal UI (52 lines)
        ├── group.js        # Group logic (87 lines)
        ├── char.js         # Character logic (116 lines)
        ├── inventory.js    # Inventory logic (75 lines)
        └── quest.js        # Quest logic (68 lines)
```

